detail.name: Golden Frieza
detail.effect:
[Double Strike] (This card inflicts 2 damage instead of 1 when attacking.)
[When Attacking] Choose up to 1 of your opponent's Rest Mode Battle Cards and it can't switch to Active Mode during your opponent's next turn.

faq.question: Can you use this card in a combo?
faq.answer: Yes, you can. You can place a Battle Card with 0 or more combo power for a combo.

faq.question: このカードでコンボすることはできますか？
faq.answer: はい、できます。コンボは０以上のコンボパワーを持つバトルカードを置くことができます。
